creator: Autumn Life Pte. Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
Autumn is currently only available to users in Singapore.

Stay On Top Of Your Finances with a single dashboard to consolidate your savings & loans, properties, CPF and investments, and your total net worth at a glance. With Autumn, you’ll always have a clear understanding of your financial health.

Understand Your Trade-offs. Don’t know if you can achieve your financial goal based on your lifestyle choices today? Autumn tells you how much you need to be saving for your future and whether you’re on track to achieving that goal. We’ll also let you know if you can afford your next big-ticket purchase.

Grow Your Wealth and have a robust nest egg when you retire. With Autumn, you get a consolidated view of all your investments, across asset classes, geographies and sectors so you can see the opportunities and gaps in your investment portfolio and maximise the potential of your money.

Autumn simplifies your financial planning.
• Get a clear view of your money across bank accounts (both local and overseas) and CPF accounts in one place.
• See all your non-cash assets such as properties and investments across regions, sectors and geographies, in one place.
• Plan for your retirement with a projection of your retirement goal based on your desired retirement income, expected retirement age, and current savings.
• Find out if your aspirations are achievable based on your retirement goal and current liabilities.
• Get personalised insights to help achieve your financial goals
• Live well today while planning for a secure future

Features:
• Overview of finances including savings & loans, properties, CPF, investments.
• Retirement Calculator
• Aspirations Tracker
•. Weekly Checklist so you keep your data up-to-date
• Highly secured data encryption. Users require to do two-factor authentication (2FA) to consolidate their banking accounts on Autumn
descriptionShort: Autumn brings together all your finances and planning options in one place.

title: Autumn

creator: Autumn Life Pte. Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
Wealth isn’t about having more stuff; it’s having more options for living. It doesn’t just mean retirement, but all the milestones and life chapters that matter to you.

Not knowing where to start? How ready are you to reach your goals? Don’t worry, we’ve got you covered!

• Future Readiness Score: With just a quick assessment, you can get a clear picture of your current financial readiness and future fund projections.
• Consolidated financial view: Get a bird’s eye view of your finances – savings, loans, CPF, insurance, and property.
• Investments options: Access diversified investment options tailored to your needs to support your goals.
• Health awareness: Learn how you can be better prepared for potential healthcare costs

Autumn makes managing, growing and protecting your money easier – so you can confidently deal with life’s ups and downs, and build the future you desire.

- Health: A new assessment that covers habits and coverage that feeds into the Future Readiness Score

- General: Bug fixes; UX enhancements

title: Autumn

creator: Autumn Life Pte. Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
Wealth isn’t about having more stuff; it’s having more options for living. It doesn’t just mean retirement, but all the milestones and life chapters that matter to you.

Not knowing where to start? How ready are you to reach your goals? Don’t worry, we’ve got you covered!

• Future Readiness Score: With just a quick assessment, you can get a clear picture of your current financial readiness and future fund projections.
• Consolidated financial view: Get a bird’s eye view of your finances – savings, loans, CPF, insurance, and property.
• Investments options: Access diversified investment options tailored to your needs to support your goals.
• Health awareness: Learn how you can be better prepared for potential healthcare costs

Autumn makes managing, growing and protecting your money easier – so you can confidently deal with life’s ups and downs, and build the future you desire.

Autumn Life Pte Ltd, the provider of the Autumn app, is regulated by the Monetary Authority of Singapore as a Licensed Financial Advisor to advise on investment products (collective investment schemes).

Our license may be viewed at: https://eservices.mas.gov.sg/fid/institution/detail/247216-AUTUMN-LIFE-PTE-LTD


Disclaimer:
General Terms and Conditions apply, see https://autumn.sg/terms-of-use/.
Invest only after you have acknowledged and accepted the risks and the terms. The images provided are for display purposes only and are not representative of actual results. This advertisement has not been reviewed by the Monetary Authority of Singapore.
